&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be the right hand to two of our leaders - the person who makes sure their time is spent on what matters, that nothing falls through the cracks, and that the day-to-day rhythm of the business runs with the same care we put into our product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll have exposure to every part of the business, and the chance to shape how a fast-growing company actually operates. We will trust you with a lot; and in return, you&#39;ll have visibility into every corner of a growing company.&lt;/p&gt;
