&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Margaux&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Margaux is a new kind of footwear brand rooted in friendship, collaboration, and community. Co-founders Sarah Pierson and Alexa Buckley launched Margaux in 2015, setting out to create a modern footwear wardrobe for women on the go, powered by thoughtful design and an innovative approach. What started as a handful of silhouettes has grown into a full collection, complete with beautiful, comfortable styles for everywhere life takes you. Each pair is designed in New York and handmade in Spain, and thoughtfully crafted to withstand the test of time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Margaux is seeking an exemplary store manager to join our team opening a new store at Marin Country Mart. The manager will work closely with the Margaux HQ team to ensure the successful launch of the new location and subsequently will be responsible for all aspects of managing the store.&lt;/p&gt;
