&lt;p&gt;This location will initially operate as a one-year pop-up, offering a unique opportunity to introduce and grow the Margaux brand within the Marin community. The Store Manager will play a critical role in establishing the store as a destination, building local relationships, and driving awareness throughout the duration of the pop-up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The store opening is scheduled for &lt;strong&gt;August 14th&lt;/strong&gt;; however, the manager will have an &lt;strong&gt;immediate start date&lt;/strong&gt; and will be an essential team member ahead of the opening, facilitating the seamless launch of the new store.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position offers a unique opportunity to join Margaux at an exciting stage of growth and offers the candidate an opportunity for leadership development during the brand’s retail expansion.&lt;/p&gt;
